## Reproducing Results
1. Download the Power Plant Satellite Imagery Dataset from Data Ninja (large download).
2. Unzip locally and run:   GeoTIFF_preprocessing_local in Notebooks folder
3. Zip the processed dataset as:   ds_small.zip  and place it in your local Downloads folder.
4. Download WRI Global Power Plant Database v1.3 (included in Data Folder as global_power_plant_database.csv).
5. Open powerplant_deep_learning_final in Google Colab and set runtime to T4 GPU.
6. Run the notebook cell-by-cell, uploading ds_small.zip when prompted.
